                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930410-105-defend960 t17930410-105-punish577"></join>
               Permitted to go to Sea
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
